_c"></span><span class="ls13">依靠佛法可以消除，<span class="_ _18"></span><span class="ls1a">并最终得到解脱的安乐。<span class="_ _17"></span><span class="ls0"> </span></span></span></div><div class="t m0 xc h4 ycc ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这个道理，<span class="_ _6"></span>你若想更深层地了解，<span class="_ _6"></span>可以看看<span class="_ _6"></span>《华严经》<span class="_ _7"></span>、</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ycd ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">《虚幻休息》等。 </div><div class="t m0 x9 h3 yeb ffe fs2 fc0 sc0 ls38 ws0">主持人<span class="ffb ls0">：<span class="_ _17"></span><span class="ff4 fs3">现在问答正式结束，<span class="_ _18"></span>有请何荣汉博士总结致辞—— </span></span></div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
